# Format
*.conf linguist-language=Nginx linguist-detectable
*.json linguist-language=JSON linguist-detectable
*.md linguist-language=Markdown linguist-detectable
*.pub linguist-language=Text linguist-detectable
*.toml linguist-language=TOML linguist-detectable

